    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. The chassis has been properly maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and upgraded bushings to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the valvetrain and bottom end are within tight tolerances. Equipped with a balanced MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, this example offers the visceral, communicative steering rack enthusiasts demand. It is a mechanically robust driver's car ready for spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
